## SQLite Bundling

rusqlite is configured with the `bundled` feature. Through `libsqlite3-sys`, thinindex compiles and links SQLite from vendored source instead of requiring a system SQLite library.

libsqlite3-sys
- Package: libsqlite3-sys
- Upstream: https://github.com/rusqlite/rusqlite
- License expression: MIT
- Bundled source status: selected indirectly by `rusqlite` with the `bundled` feature.
- SQLite source status: the bundled SQLite source is documented by upstream SQLite as public domain.
- Accepted reason: reproducible cross-platform SQLite behavior without a system SQLite dependency.
- Notice/source text: referenced from the crate package, rusqlite upstream repository, and upstream SQLite copyright page.

